abstract: As the co-working giant struggles with a cool reception to the forthcoming stock sale, one of its biggest investors, SoftBank, reportedly wants the deal postponed.
snippet: As the co-working giant struggles with a cool reception to the forthcoming stock sale, one of its biggest investors, SoftBank, reportedly wants the deal postponed.
lead_paragraph: Good Tuesday. On today’s agenda: Apple’s annual iPhone unveiling is scheduled for 1 p.m. Eastern. (Was this email forwarded to you? Sign up here.)

abstract: The presidential hopefuls detailed their views on the limits of executive power in response to a New York Times survey.
snippet: The presidential hopefuls detailed their views on the limits of executive power in response to a New York Times survey.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Democratic presidential candidates broadly agree that President Trump has shaken the presidency loose from its constitutional limits and say that the White House needs major new legal curbs, foreshadowing a potential era of reform akin to the post-Watergate period if any of them wins next year’s election.
